reviewText: If you haven't seen Holmes do a home inspection, you are missing an interesting view of a very important task. You WILL learn from each episode, pretty much guaranteed. If you are looking at purchasing a home anytime soon, get this series, watch this series, study this series. It will open your eyes, and make you a much smarter buyer.
Mike Holmes is my "learn how to do it right" DIY hero.
We love this series and have learned so much!!!!

Mike Holmes is the master of home repair and remodeling. He has all the experience to know how not to do it. He shares
his experience with complete detail making sure you don't make the same mistakes.
